room_title: Escape room "The Gallery" by NC Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: I had a great time playing the Gallery. Although the room can fit up to ten players, we did it with just four and escaped. What awesome puzzles!

room_title: Escape room "The Gallery" by NC Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: I was invited for my friend's birthday and we did The Gallery Room. Man, that was so much fun! We made it out in time, which we are all proud of! I am definitely going to try to come back with my family to try this out with them.

room_title: Escape room "The Gallery" by NC Escape in Raleigh - Durham
review: This place is awesome. This was our first time doing an escape room and I can't wait till next time. We completed the Gallery in 53 minutes with four people. Next time I want to try Ex Machina. I will bring my 15-year-old son next time. He will love it!
